(75, '2021-07-08 05:43:53', 'Müller', 'Paul Müller', '13', '|eher positiv|', 'The mix between exercises and lecture was very well balanced. I would like to see more examples of requirements at each abstraction level and especially comparison between good and bad.', '|sehr gut|', 'Holding and whole day online training requires a lot preparation and planning, as keeping people focused in front of PC in online meeting is very hard. Before the training I was afraid that it will be hard to sit in a training for such long time, but eventually there was no problem. This is because a good balance between involving exercises and lectures.', '|eher positiv|', '', '', '', 'Vielen Dank and Herr Muller fur ein echt gutes Job.', '|eher positiv|', '|Architektur & Modellierung||Programmierung & Code||Testen & Qualitätssicherung||Projekt-& Produktmanagement||User Experience|', NULL),
