(254, '2021-11-09 15:30:56', 'holzweber', 'Dominic Holzweber', '11', '|sehr gut|', 'More interactive exercises with refactoring and coding would be preferable to having a look at one giant class on github I think. ', '|sehr gut|', 'Very lively and upbeat. Enjoyable speed and tonality. Overall a very good presenter.', '|sehr gut|', 'Nothing to complain about', 'The information was relevant and useful!', 'Please, please, please show the higher-ups the software we could use as a team instead of us the developers. Things like TeamScale are nice to know about but useless as a tool if the company doesn\"t know about it.', 'Come back soon!', '|eher positiv|', '|Agile Methoden||Architektur & Modellierung||Programmierung & Code||Testen & Qualitätssicherung||Informationssicherheit & Datenschutz||Management & Prozesse||Projekt-& Produktmanagement||Requirements Engineering||User Experience||Testautomatisierung|', NULL),
