(277, '2021-11-12 13:19:01', 'Schiller', 'Franz Schiller', '2', '|sehr gut|', 'Nothing specific . The overall experience is well balanced. Looking forward for future trainings', '|sehr gut|', 'Very consistent and well maintained levels of moderation. I enjoyed his explanation.', '|sehr gut|', '', 'Size of participants, Overall content and the trainer', 'May be more exercises and practical examples ', '', '|eher positiv|', '|Requirements Engineering||User Experience|', NULL),
(278, '2021-11-12 15:22:09', 'Christmann', 'Stephan Christmann', '2', '|sehr gut|', '- Stephan has a high knowledge on the topics, and he had good presentation skills. As a suggestion I would recommend to have some material related to Automotive Industry AUTOSAR Architecture just as a reference for attendees to help them understand many of the topics shown on the training. ', '|sehr gut|', 'Stephan has a high knowledge on the topics, moreover he has great presentation skills. I like the way he presented the information during the 4-day training.', '|eher positiv|', 'Overall experience was great, however I would recommend Software Quality Lab to offer perhaps a 8-day training to allow session to be shorter. I believe 8 hours daily is too intensive, I would like a 4 hours daily format more.', 'Exercises were great, they really helped to understand the technical topics.Stephan is a knowledgeable trainer and has great presentation skills.', 'A 8-day\"s format of the training would be preffered, where daily session can be reduced from 8 hours to 4 hours.', 'Overall Training Experience was great :)', '|sehr gut|', '|Architektur & Modellierung||Requirements Engineering|', NULL),
(279, '2021-11-13 08:41:56', 'Müller', 'Paul Müller', '13', '|sehr gut|', 'Gut vorbereitete Seminarinhalte, welche hinsichtlich der Schwerpunkte individuell auf den Wissensstand der Teilnehmer vertieft wurden.', '|sehr gut|', '', '|sehr gut|', '', 'Vertiefung der theoretischen Inhalte mit den Praxisbeispielen ist meines Erachtens gut gelungen. Insbesondere auch, dass Beispiele aus dem Berufsalltag diskuttiert wurden.', 'Ggf. noch mehr Praxisbeispiele aus dem jeweiligen Arbeitsumfeld der Teilnehmer integrieren.', '', '|sehr gut|', '|Management & Prozesse||Projekt-& Produktmanagement||Requirements Engineering|', NULL),
