(297, '2021-11-19 08:46:50', 'Christmann', 'Stephan Christmann', '2', '|eher positiv|', 'Good seminar with very good exercises.The slide set could be improved still:Whenever it was listing multiple things (for example all patterns, ...), information was spread over many, many pages. I summarized these and learned using my own notes instead. Going through all slides each time would not have worked well.', '|sehr gut|', 'Very good trainer, enthusiastic, friendly, knows what he talks about, flexible with our wishes. Perfect!', '|eher positiv|', 'All good.', 'Our trainer let us come up with questions each day for the next morning and prepared different extra exercises that helped to learn facts much better than with just reading slides alone would. He was very flexible shifting around exercises to fit our needs.', 'Use less slides and summarize them more. Or even better, after chapters with long lists of items (like patterns for example) list them all again in short words at the end. There are summaries at the end of chapters already but they do not list all important facts shortly but only a few. Maybe also provide a document with text that one can learn with rather than slides (such a document was available for the ISTQB Certified Tester Foundation Level for example).', '', '|sehr gut|', '|Architektur & Modellierung||Testen & Qualitätssicherung||Requirements Engineering||Testautomatisierung|', NULL),
(298, '2021-11-19 09:16:37', 'holzweber', 'Dominic Holzweber', '2', '|eher positiv|', '', '|eher positiv|', '', '|eher positiv|', '', 'Well organised, very interactive', 'Slides can be improved and also more real time application examples during the session. ', '', '|eher positiv|', '|Architektur & Modellierung|', NULL),
