(300, '2021-11-22 09:21:35', 'holzweber', 'Dominic Holzweber', '2', '|sehr gut|', '* The structure (headlines) of the slides were a bit confusing* Participants were given slides slightly different to the ones the presenter used', '|sehr gut|', '* Very competent* Very friendly* Very engaging and involving', '|sehr gut|', '* There weren\"t many touch points for me as the booking of the course was done by my company\"s purchase department', '* That the trainer really took the time to answer all questions and explain* My co-participants were very experienced so the discussion was great and interesting', '* Providing signposts on the slides to keep the structure of the seminar clear', 'Thank you! I am very satisfied with the whole course.', '|sehr gut|', '', NULL),
