(402, '2022-02-04 13:06:17', 'Schiller', 'Franz Schiller', '2', '|sehr gut|', 'Excercises on the first and second day were quite good, but after that only discussions were done and no more views or real collaboration. Make it more practical to the end please.', '|sehr gut|', 'Very profound english language skills!', '|sehr gut|', 'Really nice organisation of the seminar.', '- Nice atmosphere for an online seminar- Trainer gave a lot examples of his own practical career', '- More practical excercises please', '', '|eher positiv|', '|Architektur & Modellierung|', NULL),
