(468, '2022-04-01 10:30:31', 'Synka', 'Josef Synka', '1', '|sehr gut|', '', '|sehr gut|', 'Josef was extremely helpful answering questions and explaining concepts in simple terms. Also gave examples during presentation which was easier to relate and understand the topic. Revisions from the previous day chapters was helpful. ', '|sehr gut|', '', '', 'May be the training could be divided into 6 days or 8 days considering only first half of the day or second half of the day. Because Full day training continuously for 8 hours is little exhausting.', '', '|sehr gut|', '|Agile Methoden||Testen & Qualitätssicherung||Testautomatisierung|', NULL),
