(586, '2022-07-14 22:03:51', 'Christmann', 'Stephan Christmann', '2', '|sehr gut|', 'Lots of good information. I wish there was more time to go deeper into the architectural designs.', '|sehr gut|', 'Stefan answered questions attentively and explained most everything thoroughly ', '|eher positiv|', 'This is my only interaction with Software Quality Lab so far', 'I enjoyed the exercises they were helpful to understand concepts better', 'A bit more explanation of what is expected for the exercises. Example answers to look at afterwards', '', '|sehr gut|', '|Architektur & Modellierung|', NULL),
